New look! New features!
The new i-Akaun mobile application offers an enhanced user interface and simpler layout to make your browsing and viewing experience easier and faster.
Members can also enjoy additional features such as viewing selected posts from EPF Facebook, accessing withdrawal eligibility information and receiving important messages and notifications.
